      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 59,
      "message": "This looks like a good candidate for a method.\n\nsetProperty(String key, String value) {\n  if (!System.getProperties().containsKey(key)) {\n     System.setProperty(key, value);\n  }\n}\n\nand then \n\nsetProperty(TRUSTSTORE_PROPERTY_NAME, CassandraUtils.getTruststore());\n\nand so on.\n\nAnother such method for boolean.\n\nIt can be even made more efficient (avoid unnecessary initialization/calls) using functional:\n\nsetProperty(String key, Supplier<String> supplier) {\n  if (!System.getProperties().containsKey(key)) {\n     System.setProperty(supplier.get());\n  }\n}\n\nand setProperty(TRUSTSTORE_PROPERTY_NAME, () -> CassandraUtils.getTruststore());",
      "author": {
